quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  66,0,shuru allah ka naam le kar jo bara meharban nihayat reham wala hai
  66,1,ae paighambar jo cheez khuda ne tumahray liye jaaiz ki hai tum is se kinara kashi kyun karte ho? (kiya is se ) apni biwion ki khushnodi chahtay ho? aur khuda bakhsnay wala meharban hai
  66,2,khuda ne tum logon ke liye tumhari qasmon ka kaffara muqarrar kardiya hai. aur khuda hi tumhara karsaaz hai. aur woh Dana ( aur ) hikmat wala hai
  66,3,aur ( yaad karo ) jab paighambar ne apni aik bi bi se aik bhaid ki baat kahi to ( is ne doosri ko bta di ). jab is ne is ko Afshakiya aur khuda ne is ( haal ) se paighambar ko aagah kardiya to paighambar ne un ( bi bi ko woh baat ) kuch to batayi aur kuch nah batayi. to jab woh un ko jitayee to poochnay lagen ke aap ko kis ne bataya? unhon ne kaha ke mujhe is ne bataya hai jo jan-nay wala khabardaar hai
  66,4,agar tum dono khuda ke agay tauba karo ( to behtar hai kyunkay ) tumahray dil kaj hogaye hain. aur agar paighambar ( ki aeza ) par baahum eaanat karo gi to khuda aur Jibreel aur naik kirdaar musalman un ke haami ( aur Dostdar ) hain. aur un ke ilawa ( aur ) farishtay bhi madadgaar hain
  66,5,"agar paighambar tum ko Talaq day den to ajab nahi ke un ka perwar-digaar tumahray badlay un ko tum se behtar bibiyanday day. musalman, sahib imaan farmanbardar tauba karne waleyan ibadat guzar roza rakhnay waleyan ban shohar aur kanwariyan"
  66,6,momino! apne aap ko aur apne ahal Ayal ko aatish ( jahannum ) se bachao jis ka eendhan aadmi aur pathar hain aur jis par tund khoo aur sakht mizaaj farishtay ( muqarrar ) hain jo irshad khuda un ko farmata hai is ki nafarmani nahi karte aur jo hukum un ko milta hai usay baja laatay hain
  66,7,kafroo! aaj bahanay mat banaao. jo amal tumkiya karte ho un hi ka tum ko badla diya jaye ga
  66,8,momino! khuda ke agay saaf dil se tauba karo. umeed hai ke woh tumahray gunah tum se daur kar day ga aur tum ko baghaye bahisht mein jin ke neechay nehrain beh rahi hain daakhil kere ga. is din paighambar ko aur un logon ko jo un ke sath imaan laaye hain ruswa nahi kere ga ( balkay ) un ka noor imaan un ke agay aur dahni taraf ( roshni karta howa ) chal raha hoga. aur woh khuda se iltija karen ge ke ae perwar-digaar hamara noor hamaray liye poora kar aur hamein maaf karna. be shak khuda har cheez par Qadir hai
  66,9,ae paighambar! kafiroon aur mnafqon se lrho aur un par sakhti karo. un ka thikana dozakh hai. aur woh bohat buri jagah hai
  66,10,khuda ne kafiroon ke liye Nooh ki biwi aur loot ki biwi ki misaal bayan farmai hai. dono hamaray do naik bundon ke ghar mein theen aur dono ne un ki khayanat ki to woh khuda ke muqablay mein aur un aurton ke kuch bhi kaam nah aeye aur un ko hukum diya gaya ke aur daakhil honay walon ke sath tum bhi dozakh mein daakhil ho jao
  66,11,aur mominon ke liye ( aik ) misaal ( to ) firaon ki biwi ki bayan farmai ke is ne khuda se iltija ki ke ae mere perwar-digaar mere liye bahisht mein apne paas aik ghar bana aur mujhe firaon aur is ke aamaal ( zasht maal ) se nijaat bakhash aur zalim logon ke haath se mujh ko mukhlasi ataa farma
  66,12,aur ( doosri ) Imran ki beti maryam ki jinhon ne apni sharum gah ko mehfooz rakha to hum ne is mein apni rooh phoonk di aur apne perwar-digaar ke kalaam aur is ki kitabon ko barhaq samjhti theen aur farmabardaron mein se theen
